86
00:07:05,928 --> 00:07:06,905
And he calls you.

87
00:07:07,135 --> 00:07:07,880
Yeah.

88
00:07:09,499 --> 00:07:11,092
So you've been talking
to my father...

89
00:07:11,093 --> 00:07:13,105
