Docket number 178649325.

159
00:10:29,215 --> 00:10:31,730
The charge is second-degree
assault, Your Honor.

160
00:10:31,731 --> 00:10:36,152
At 6 p.m. yesterday, in a bar and grill
at 50210th Avenue...

161
00:10:36,153 --> 00:10:38,119
Mr. McMullen assaulted...

162
00:10:38,611 --> 00:10:40,099
An off-duty policeman.

163
00:10:40,324 --> 00:10:43,674
Well, I'd love to hear about this
in your own words, Mr...

164
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:45,158
McMullen.

165
00:10:46,143 --> 00:10:47,307
Your Honor...

166
00:10:47,845 --> 00:10:50,086
I'm a victim of police brutality.

167
00:10:50,087 --> 00:10:52,472
Just tell us what occurred,
Mr. McMullen.

168
00:10:53,526 --> 00:10:54,674
Well...

169
00:10:55,041 --> 00:10:57,206
It all happened so fast,
Your Honor.

170
00:10:57,861 --> 00:10:59,222
I'll try to remember.

171
00:11:00,204 --> 00:11:01,495
We had an argument.

172
00:11:01,558 --> 00:11:03,142
To be fair about it...

173
00:11:03,416 --> 00:11:05,479
I was as much at fault
as he was.

174
00:11:06,511 --> 00:11:08,665
Well, one thing led
to another and...

175
00:11:08,666 --> 00:11:10,024
Somehow it comes out...

176
00:11:10,025 --> 00:11:12,174
That my mother was
a Native American...

177
00:11:12,818 --> 00:11:14,792
A full-blooded Cherokee,
Your Honor.

178
00:11:15,737 --> 00:11:17,760
And this policeman yells...

179
00:11:17,885 --> 00:11:21,095
"It's too bad Custer made such
a half-ass job of it."

180
00:11:22,037 --> 00:11:23,572
Well, I lost control.

181
00:11:24,142 --> 00:11:25,327
What did you do?

182
00:11:25,718 --> 00:11:28,745
I did what little I could
for a man my age.

183
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:32,709
The little Mr. McMullen was able to do seems
to have been pretty effective, Your Honor.

184
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:37,195
The officer has taken 18 stitches
in his face, his nose is broken...

185
00:11:37,196 --> 00:11:38,909
And his jaw is wired up.

186
00:11:39,313 --> 00:11:41,416
