than I knew.

187
00:11:41,417 --> 00:11:43,877
it was fright, fear, whatever it was,
Your Honor.

188
00:11:43,878 --> 00:11:47,188
Your Honor, here is the BCI
on Mr. Jessie McMullen.

189
00:11:47,189 --> 00:11:53,244
It begins in 1947 with a three-year term
for assault just after he was naturalized.

190
00:11:53,642 --> 00:11:56,348
It goes on and on and on and...

191
