192
00:11:58,158 --> 00:12:00,885
Before the prosecutor
sentences my client...

193
00:12:00,886 --> 00:12:02,823
Perhaps he will agree to a trial?

194
00:12:03,904 --> 00:12:05,620
We're only here to set bail.

195
00:12:06,351 --> 00:12:09,760
I'd like to point out that the defendant's
grandson is present in court.

196
00:12:10,013 --> 00:12:12,140
My client has roots in this community.

197
00:12:12,932 --> 00:12:15,855
Bail is set at 5,000 dollars.

198
00:12:15,856 --> 00:12:19,668
A 500-dollar cash bail
bond is acceptable.

199
00:12:20,858 --> 00:12:22,127
Next.

200
00:12:22,223 --> 00:12:26,353
Docket number 178649326.

201
00:12:26,614 --> 00:12:27,917
Did you bring the 500?

202
00:12:30,432 --> 00:12:32,059
You don't travel light, I see.

203
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,698
Vito gave me 800.

204
00:12:33,724 --> 00:12:35,130
Good thing he had the cash.

205
00:12:35,131 --> 00:12:38,230
Your father's always got a few grand
swag money in his pocket.

206
00:12:38,408 --> 00:12:40,501
He robs the tax collector,
your father.

207
00:12:40,936 --> 00:12:43,730
It's never been easy for me
having a thief in the family.

208
00:12:44,705 --> 00:12:45,908
You've grown, Adam.

209
00:12:46,356 --> 00:12:47,761
It's been a long time.

210
00:12:52,970 --> 00:12:54,054
Money.

211
00:12:54,361 --> 00:12:55,523
Oh, money.

212
00:13:03,143 --> 00:13:04,218
Look at this.

213
00:13:04,463 --> 00:13:05,921
It's become a shithouse.

214
00:13:06,433 --> 00:13:08,060
Never been in a jail before.

215
00:13:08,061 --> 00:13:10,078
You haven't missed an awful lot.

216
00:13:10,104 --> 00:13:12,330
It's got some good points too,
when you're young.

217
00:13:12,331 --> 00:13:13,202
Like what?

218
00:13:13,203 --> 00:13:14,592
It can help build character...

219
00:13:14,593 --> 00:13:15,999
Like a hitch in the Army.

220
00:13:16,831 --> 00:13:19,640
A wallet. A watch.
A handkerchief, pure silk.

221
00:13:19,747 --> 00:13:22,171
Not to mention 270,000 dollars.

222
00:13:22,390 --> 00:13:24,528
I'm just kidding. 270 dollars.

223
00:13:25,654 --> 00:13:26,702
Hey, Jessie!

224
00:13:26,709 --> 00:13:27,619
Hi, John!

225
00:13:27,620 --> 00:13:29,194
