230
00:13:40,915 --> 00:13:42,246
And they don't, Jessie.

231
00:13:42,488 --> 00:13:44,295
They really don't agree with me at all.

232
00:13:45,461 --> 00:13:48,436
Last night in the bar,
did that cop land the first punch?

233
00:13:48,821 --> 00:13:51,045
Adam, I've never been
in a bar fight yet...

234
00:13:51,046 --> 00:13:53,046
