landed the first punch.

235
00:13:53,072 --> 00:13:55,309
It's a sure recipe for losing.

236
00:13:56,629 --> 00:13:58,170
So when did you
get back in town?

237
00:13:58,572 --> 00:14:00,272
I left school in January.

238
00:14:01,116 --> 00:14:04,397
I was this far away from getting
my master's in molecular biology.

239
00:14:04,643 --> 00:14:06,342
And your old man's
paying for all this?

240
00:14:06,553 --> 00:14:08,317
No way. I'm on
full scholarship.

241
00:14:08,803 --> 00:14:10,503
I was a Westinghouse Scholar.

242
00:14:11,117 --> 00:14:13,316
It's a big deal.
They only have six each year.

243
00:14:14,292 --> 00:14:15,350
I hated it.

244
00:14:15,673 --> 00:14:17,309
It felt worse than that cell.

245
00:14:18,110 --> 00:14:20,420
They've got your whole life
mapped out for you.

246
00:14:21,085 --> 00:14:22,438
You don't know the half of it.

